column5: Looks like a good day.  Was that the north shore?
Nice going, fingers crossed but it's shaping up to be a better year than the last few.
Who needs a net anyways right?
Who needs a net anyways right? lol. Always forget something on the first trip of the year.  The no net challenge and we never lost one because of it.
I have to say I have never brought in a fish with the Barn door open. Nice day you had. Beauty boat too.
